cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.RO 

The paper deals with local image descriptors and their optimization for GPU processing. This is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) research. The paper also evaluates the performance of the proposed method in a structure from motion (SfM) application, which falls under robotics (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. Finally, the use of CUDA technology suggests that the paper may also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) research.
